reviewText: Didn't work properly would always restart when put back in, wouldn't play past episode 3, not really worth buying.

Slightly dissapointed. I'm not sure why but this disc set will blur out some of the gore and occasionally runs Japanese text across the screen. The season 1 standalone disc I have does not. It seems "bootleggy" but legit at the same time. I'm not an expert on cartoons, that's just my take, there may be a valid reason to it all
